  "texts": [
    "A t ð Þ and B t ð Þ are matrix functions whose values may be time-dependent but not state-dependent.",
    "This model simplification, in conjunction with a quadratic objective, reduces (3.1) to a quadratic program, a convex problem that even embedded devices can solve quickly.",
    "However, a simpler model will necessarily lead to predictions of lower accuracy, and thereby worse performance.",
    "If we do not wish to simplify the model, an alternative is to develop explicit MPC controllers (Drgoňa et al., 2013; Klaučo and Kvasnica, 2014; Parisio et al., 2014).",
    "The key idea is to drive some close-form solution for the MPC problem and then identify the parameterized control outputs online."
  ]
